FBIS4-24220 "drafr123_d_94013" FBIS-AFR-94-123 Daily Report 25 Jun 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Mozambique New Party, Mozambique Democratic Alliance, Formed New Party, Mozambique Democratic Alliance, Formed MB2606052394 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 1730 GMT 25 Jun 94 MB2606052394 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network Portuguese BFN [Text] A new political party has been created in the country. It is called the Mozambique Democratic Alliance, ADM. According to a document sent to our news desk, the ADM intends to build a state on the rule of law, based on the principles enshrined in he Human Rights Charter and the Convention on Prevention of Crimes of Genocide. The ADM Party says it defends equal opportunities for all Mozambicans in all fields of social life.
